name: Joe Bryant
bio: Ethan is a freaky frontend enthusiast who has a passion for music and mathematics. He loves to grind, to run around Bel Air and admire the beautiful mansions, and to debone chicken wings. When he has free time he also loves to show his friends his special sauce.
Other hobbies include: pregaming din tai fung with shake shack, being nonCHALANT, and celebrating the month of May.
